Cost of Synchronization Primitives
==================================

This project is for performance and scalability test of synchronization
primitives including memory barrier, atomic operations, mutex, etc.


Build & Usage
=============

Follow below instructions to build and execute the test.
```
$ make
$ ./cost_of_sync_primitives
```

Following command will generate a pdf format plot.  Note that this command
requires 'lazybox'[1] to be installed  on your home directory.
```
$ make report
```


